"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-12-02-Athens-exhibition-celebrates-China-s-Double-Olympics-host-status--1yXz162Vdfi-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evangelo Sipsas in Athens  Copied  In the heart of Athens, at the Serafio Museum, Chinese traditions and Olympic history converged in a dazzling exhibition celebrating Beijing's unique achievement as the only city to host both the Summer and Winter Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 224, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999999993824531, \"rank\": 6.171867386902149e-10, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9999999993824531, \"rank\": 6.171867386902149e-10, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"score\": 0.7259416153185818, \"rank\": 0.3278369345152073, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"score\": 0.9999239492765726, \"rank\": 7.60564209429857e-05, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event attracted a diverse audience and highlighted the enduring bond between Greece and China.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999652329757105, \"rank\": 3.3741024565958325e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999981939570655, \"rank\": 1.5527490001673145e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kung Fu warriors and Tai Chi masters enthralled visitors with performances set to traditional Chinese music, creating an immersive cultural experience.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_martial_arts\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.682227968282815e-13, \"text\": \"Kung Fu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_martial_arts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_martial_arts\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tai_chi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1186886059015941e-34, \"text\": \"Tai Chi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tai_chi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tai_chi\"}, {\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9999999999654392, \"rank\": 3.443915634935388e-11, \"text\": \"traditional Chinese music\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The exhibition, aptly named 'Double Olympics,' brought together artists, political leaders, business professionals, and members of the Greek community to explore the significance of cultural exchange.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9992130829574553, \"rank\": 0.0004530907529721329, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This event highlights the natural connections between cultures,\\\" Greek visitor Kostas, toldCGTN.\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9992130829574553, \"rank\": 0.0004530907529721329, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Despite our differences, we share much in common.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's refreshing to see such positivity amidst the often-negative headlines.\\\"\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Historic milestone  Organized by the Beijing Olympic City Development Association (BODA), the exhibition celebrated China's historic Olympic milestones\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094hosting the 2008 Summer Games and the 2022 Winter Games.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"score\": 0.9999239492765726, \"rank\": 7.60564209429857e-05, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}, {\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999981939570655, \"rank\": 1.5527490001673145e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It featured Olympic memorabilia, iconic photographs from the opening and closing ceremonies, and intricate Chinese artworks that inspired the Games' designs.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"score\": 0.7259416153185818, \"rank\": 0.3278369345152073, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attendees were also treated to live demonstrations of Chinese cultural traditions, including calligraphy, tea ceremonies, and paper cutting.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"score\": 0.7259416153185818, \"rank\": 0.3278369345152073, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These interactive experiences allowed visitors to connect deeply with the richness of Chinese heritage, creating a tangible cultural bridge between Greece and China.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"score\": 0.7259416153185818, \"rank\": 0.3278369345152073, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999652329757105, \"rank\": 3.3741024565958325e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999981939570655, \"rank\": 1.5527490001673145e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Monica Shuxian Yu, manager of the 'Double Olympics' Expo, explained the choice of Greece for this showcase.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monica_Geller\", \"score\": 0.9999968963154932, \"rank\": 2.304078924483151e-06, \"text\": \"Monica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monica_Geller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monica_Geller\"}, {\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999652329757105, \"rank\": 3.3741024565958325e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meaningful economic collaboration  \\\"As the birthplace of the Olympics, Greece holds unique global significance.\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999652329757105, \"rank\": 3.3741024565958325e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through this exhibition, visitors can explore and connect with Chinese culture,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.07860491925222e-19, \"text\": \"Chinese culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond the vibrant displays and performances, the exhibition also underscored the broader implications of cultural exchanges.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Investments do not happen spontaneously.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They result from long-term cultural, ideological, and interpersonal interactions,\\\" Ioannis Georgizas, CEO of the Serafio Complex, told CGTN.\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Events like this pave the way for meaningful economic collaboration.\\\"\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the exhibition concluded, it left a lasting impression on all who attended.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a celebration not just of Beijing's Olympic legacy but of the growing opportunities for mutual understanding and cooperation between Greece and China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a testament to the enduring power of cultural diplomacy.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"score\": 0.9999239492765726, \"rank\": 7.60564209429857e-05, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}, {\"begin\": 2749, \"end\": 2755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999652329757105, \"rank\": 3.3741024565958325e-05, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the 